resources.string: Aksesibiliti savis dɛn dɔn ɛnabul bɔt dɛn nɔ de rɔn, yu kin tray fɔ ɛnabul bak ɔ stat yu fon bak
Fail fɔ ɛnabul aksesibiliti savis wit rut prɛvilɛj
Yuz wan fɔgrɔn savis fɔ mek yu ap kɔntinyu fɔ wok
Aksesibiliti savis wok dɛn fɔ ɛnabul fɔ ɛksɛkutiv (rizɔv) .
Yu fɔ opin di winda we de flɔt fɔ si di lɔg (we dɛn dɔn kip) .
Volume up key de stɔp ɔl di skript dɛn
Afta yu opin, we yu rɔn di skript go opin di aksesibiliti savis ɔtomɛtik wan wit Rut prɛvilɛj dɛn (aytem we dɛn dɔn kip) .
Ɔtomɛtik ɛnabul savis dɛn wit rut prɛvilɛj dɛn
Layout analysis kin stebul mɔ we dɛn ɛnabul, bɔt smɔl nɔmba pan skript dɛn nɔ kin wok fayn. Ristart aksesibiliti savis fɔ tek ɛfɛkt
Rɔn di skript dairekt afta yu dɔn opin di ap
Di lɔg intafays nɔ de sho, ɛn dɛn nid fɔ sɔpɔt skript fɔ opin dis intafays nɛks tɛm

Di softwe nid fɔ opin \"Accessibility Services\" fɔ rɔn, duya opin \"Settings->Accessibility Services\" ɔ \"Settings->Accessibility Services->More Downloaded Services\", fɛn \" %s \", ɛn ɛnabul Aksesibiliti Savis dɛn
Aksesibiliti savis dɛn nid fɔ ɛnabul
